# Blog & MDX Guidelines

## Content Locations
- English posts: [content/](mdc:content)
- Chinese posts: [content/zh/](mdc:content/zh)
- Images: [public/blogs/images/](mdc:public/blogs/images)

## Rendering Pipeline
- MDX processing and utilities: [src/lib/blog.ts](mdc:src/lib/blog.ts)
- Markdown/MDX components: [src/components/react-markdown.tsx](mdc:src/components/react-markdown.tsx)
- Blog utilities: `getPost()`, `getBlogPosts()`, `hasChineseVersion()` functions

## Authoring Conventions
- Use frontmatter for title, date, summary, and tags.
- Keep slugs URL-safe; use hyphens.
- Prefer relative image paths rooted at `/blogs/images`.
- Mathematical notation is supported (KaTeX) as needed.

## Performance & SEO
- Provide `alt` text for all images.
- Use headings hierarchy properly (one h1 per post from frontmatter).
- Avoid embedding personal information in MDX.
- Use `markdownToHTML()` for processing with KaTeX and syntax highlighting.

